<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="moreover-adv">moreover <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /mɔːr'əʊvə(r)/    美 /mɔːr'oʊvər/  </p>
<p>[句子副词] [正式用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-in-addition-furthermore">1.★ <strong>再者；而且 (in addition / furthermore)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don’t like skating; moreover, the ice is too thin. 
我不喜欢溜冰；而且，这冰也太薄了。</p></div></div>